cn.inbot.padbotsdk

Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.inbot.padbotsdk.Robot

  • public class Robot
extends java.lang.Object

    Robot Model Class

    After connected the robot, you can get an instance of this class. You can get the robot information by the instance.

    Author : Inbot
    Create Date : 2017/5/11
    JDK version used : JDK1.8
    Version : V3.0.0
